#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:5
msgid "Glow"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:7
msgid ""
"This effect makes parts of an image glow brighter by working on the "
"luminance channel of an image. The *Glow* is the superposition of the base "
"image and a modified version, where bright areas are blurred."
msgstr ""
"Cet effet rend des portions de l'image plus lumineuses en travaillant sur le "
"canal de luminance d'une image. Le *Glow* est la superposition d'une image "
"de base avec une version modifiée, dans laquelle les zones lumineuses sont "
"floutées."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:12
msgid ""
"To \"animate\" the glow effect, mix it with the base image using the Gamma "
"Cross effect, crossing from the base image to the glowing one."
msgstr ""
"Pour \"animer\" l'effet *Glow*, mélangez-le à l'image de base en utilisant "
"l'effet *Gamma Cross*, en passant de l'image de base à celui avec l'effet "
"*Glow*."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:18
msgid "Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:20
msgid "Threshold"
msgstr "Threshold (seuil)"

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:21
msgid "Areas brighter than the *Threshold* are blurred."
msgstr "Les zones sont lumineuses que le *Threshold* sont floutées. "

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:22
msgid "Clamp"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:23
msgid "The maximum luminosity that is added."
msgstr "La luminosité maximale qui est ajoutée."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:24
msgid "Boost Factor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:25
msgid "Multiplier of the brightness."
msgstr "Multiplicateur de la luminosité."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:26
msgid "Blur Distance"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:27
msgid "The size of the blur."
msgstr "La taille du flou."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:28
msgid "Quality"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:29
msgid ""
"Improves the quality of the glow by giving smoother results but will be "
"slower."
msgstr ""
"Améliore la qualité du *glow* en donnant des résultats plus lisses mais qui "
"seront plus lents à rendre."

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:33
msgid "Only boost"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/vse/sequencer/strips/effects/glow.rst:31
msgid ""
"This checkbox allows you to only show/use the \"modified\" version of the "
"image, without the base one."
msgstr ""
"Cette case à cocher vous permet de montrer/utiliser uniquement la version "
"\"modifiée\" de l'image, sans celle de base."

